data.description: A peaceful oasis nestled at the end of a private road located just outside the charming Historic Downtown Centerville square. This custom built, solid brick home sits on 1 acre and boasts a 2 car garage on the main level, as well as an additional garage with a workshop attached to the full finished basement below. Inside you will find rich hardwood floors and bright windows with custom plantation shutters flooding tons of natural light into this spacious home. With the master suite, formal dining room and half bathroom on the main level, two bedrooms with a Jack & Jill bathroom on the upper level, and a full finished basement on the lower level-this home truly has it all. Freshly painted with modern hardware and lighting, Samsung Smart Stainless Steel appliances, and under cabinet lighting. The lower back deck features a 24’ above ground pool with a brand new liner and robotic cleaner. Main level HVAC unit replaced in 2020. $2,000 credit for buyers.
